name: craftsman-147-sqm
description: A 17.6 x 12.4 meter single-level rach style home thoughtfully designed to provide comfort, practicality, and balanced living spaces. The layout includes three well-proportioned bedrooms and two bathrooms, offering privacy and convenience for families or guests. A dedicated living room creates a welcoming space for relaxation, while the kitchen and separate dining room support both everyday meals and special gatherings. The home also features a single-car garage for secure parking and storage. Enhancing its livability, a front porch adds inviting curb appeal and a pleasant entry experience, while a back porch extends the living area outdoors, ideal for casual seating, entertaining, or enjoying fresh air in a private setting.
